   5. Anaphora: 'When your rep shortcuts... When they pitch product... When they fail to execute' - Repeated beginning structure to build pattern recognition
   6. Antimetabole: 'Speed matters. But not as much as direction.' then later 'Velocity measures speed. Methodology ensures arrival.' - Reverses the concept to create memorable insight

